     H            Y.
      ****************************************************************
      *  PROGRAM    : AFFR15U                                        *
      *  WRITTEN    : 05/05/2023                                     *
      *  WRITTEN BY : LEC                                            *
      *  FUNCTION   : UPDATE TOYOTA ORDERS RECEIVED BEFORE SCHEDULE  *
      *               CHANGED.                                       *
      *--------------------------------------------------            *
      *  JW      2024.02.27 SAVE OLD BIN# IN BAKOME                  *
      ****************************************************************
     FAB#PL1D UF  E           K        DISK
      ****FAB#PP44 IF  E           K        DISK
      *
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      * SYSTEM TIME
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140WSDT
     I                                        1   60NOW
     I                                        7  140TODAY
     I                                        1   20HH
     I                                        3   40MN
     I                                        7  100YY
     I                                       11  120MM
     I                                       13  140DD
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80NYMD
     I                                        1   40NOYY
     I                                        5   60NOMM
     I                                        7   80NODD
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80BASHID
     I                                        1   40BANOYY
     I                                        5   60BANOMM
     I                                        7   80BANODD
      *
     I           SDS
     I                                        1   8 #PGM
     I                                      244 253 #WSID
     I                                      254 263 #USER
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           EFFDAT  80
      *
     C           K#1D1     KLIST
     C                     KFLD           TOKU    40
     C                     KFLD           NOYY
     C                     KFLD           NOMM
     C                     KFLD           NODD
      *
     C           K#1D2     KLIST
     C                     KFLD           TOKU
      *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      * MAIN ROUTINE
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      *
     C                     TIME           WSDT
     C                     Z-ADDEFFDAT    NYMD
     C                     Z-ADD3411      TOKU
      *
     C           K#1D1     SETLLAB#PL1D
      *
     C           *IN50     DOWEQ*OFF
     C           K#1D2     READEAB#PL1D                  50
      *
     C           *IN50     IFEQ *ON
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * if order was created before the change date, and ship date is
      *    on or after change date, bin# may need to be updated.
      *     (also must be an EDI order that has not been processed yet)
     C           BACRHZ    IFLT EFFDAT
     C           BASHID    ANDGEEFFDAT
     C           BASERL    ANDEQ*BLANKS
     C           BAEDIK    ANDEQ'E'
     C                     EXSR @GETBN
     C           BANOBN    IFNE ##BIN
     C           ##BIN     ANDNE*ZERO
     C                     EXSR @UPDBN
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      * get new bin# from toyota truck schedule file...
      *------------------------------------------------------
     C           @GETBN    BEGSR
      *
     C                     MOVELBAROUT    ROUTE  10 P
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     ##BIN   20
      *
     C           BANONY    IFEQ 323                        = NAPCK
     C                     CALL 'AB#R8N'
     C                     PARM           BAHPOS
     C                     PARM           EFFDAT
     C                     PARM           ##BIN
      *
     C                     ELSE
      *  if route isn't blank, call pgm to get bin# from new truck schd
     C           BAROUT    IFNE *BLANKS
     C                     CALL 'AB#R8M'
     C                     PARM           EFFDAT
     C                     PARM           ROUTE
     C                     PARM           ##BIN
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *------------------------------------------------------
      * update order/bin# in order file with new bin#...
      *------------------------------------------------------
     C           @UPDBN    BEGSR
      *
     C                     Z-ADD##BIN     BANOBN
     C                     Z-ADDYY        BAKOYY
     C                     Z-ADDMM        BAKOMM
     C                     Z-ADDDD        BAKODD
     C                     Z-ADDHH        BAKOHH
     C                     Z-ADDMN        BAKOSS
     C                     MOVEL'BINCHG'  BAKOME    P
JW   C                     MOVE BANOBN    BAKOME
     C                     MOVEL#PGM      BAKOPG    P
      *
     C                     Z-ADD##BIN     BANOBN
      *
     C                     UPDATAB#PP101
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *------------------------------------------------------
